OVERHEARD

"Surveys like Laylo are not accurate as they don't reflect the true situation on the ground."

(ME: If the true situation reflected on the ground is based on hakot crowds by the bus, balloons, "sibuyas,"  headless mannequins, banderitas, and flowers, eh di kayo na!)

I agree it is not only Laylo that BBM is no. 1, SWS, Pulse Asia, OCTA Research, Publicus Asia and other survey outfits shows the same results.

So mga taong na sinasabi these are not accurate, you are on experiencing cognitive dissonance.....
#UNiTeamBBMSARA #Halalan2022
